    </p>
    <p>
      Friday, Mar 27 — Midterm Exam (Part 2)
    </p>
    <p>
      Friday, Apr 17 — Objectives Quiz 3
    </p>
    <p>
      Monday, Apr 20 — Patriots’ Day (No Classes)
    </p>
